Union Assurance Advances in Colombo Trading on Stock Split Plan

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-05-10T04:19:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/union-assurance-advances-in-colombo-trading-on-stock-split-plan.html
Union Assurance Plc (UAL)  rose to a 52-week
high in Colombo trading after saying it plans to split each
share into two.  The Colombo-based insurance company rose as much as 32
percent and was trading 19.3 percent higher at 270 rupees as of
9:43 a.m. local time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
